title: 2015 Mustang GT Burnout with Gibson Headers and Mufflers
description:
The Gibson S550 Mustang GT is the AutoAnything #MarchModness champ! And like most champions, a celebratory dance is in order. Enjoy the wicked sound that this Gibson-tuned, Vortech supercharged Stinger Mustang belts out.

http://www.autoanything.com/march-modness

asset.title: 2015 Mustang GT Burnout with Gibson Headers and Mufflers
asset.description: The Gibson S550 Mustang GT needed to stretch it's legs on a sunny Friday afternoon. Equipped with the new Gibson 2" Long Tube Headers , 3" X-Pipe, and new MWA Mufflers this bad boy has a mean bark.  The Vortech Supercharger definitely gives the Ford Mustang a breath of fresh air, allowing the exhaust system to do some serious work.
asset.author: gibsonperformance
